  <para>
    Add a &layer; to the &layerset; currently being edited in the
    &layereditor;.  The command is called <quote>Add_Method</quote>
    because &layers; contain <link
    linkend="RegisteredClass-DisplayMethod"><classname>DisplayMethods</classname></link>.  
  </para>
  <para>
    <command>Add_Method</command> is executed by the GUI after closing
    the dialog box that is opened by the <guibutton>New...</guibutton>
    in the <guilabel>Display Methods</guilabel> pane of the
    &layereditor;.
  </para>

